{"tid":1014273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twins暗諷2R見識少","createTime":"2019-02-09T05:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T06:00:13.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a838fa4eb80bd86b5dada7b5a6dba31b7edcd61f","tid":1014273,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20031203/Article_ent/03ec4p30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20031203%2FArticle_ent%2F03ec4p30.jpg&h=6ad57a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二人組合Twins昨日往銅鑼灣，為「雞仔嘜」新店開幕任剪綵嘉賓，現場還有醒獅表演，吸引不少途人圍觀，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n勸盡早適應 <br />\n早前2R曾為「雞仔嘜」拍過一輯硬照相，問Twins可知此事時，其經理人霍紋希即代為回答說：「兩個都唔同性質。」 <br />\n至於有說2R的網站近日被Twins的歌迷刻意破壞一事，蔡卓妍說：「算啦！我哋做新人嗰陣時都有啦，重有反Twins聯盟㖭。」然後鍾欣桐亦接着說：「希望佢哋快啲習慣，同埋早啲適應。」其經理人又表示Twins在除夕舉行的演唱會，為遷就倒數，所以當晚會於九時半才開騷，而元旦則會在八時開騷。 <br />\n採訪：陳梅香　攝影：陳烱威"},{"pid":"bff4a46c071d6664dc6a314715f8c6cfb4517e9b","tid":1014273,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/04/2R%28Fake%29_2.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20060904133412\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F04%2F2R%2528Fake%2529_2.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20060904133412&h=0c5bfec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efd2f0fefe352d64432a8b0015af8ff1eb195cda","tid":1014273,"uid":140523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"舊新聞係超刺激"},{"pid":"d8f95d9ce532c7210b8bd22b6e6b6b63f1c71d1a","tid":1014273,"uid":117679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efd2f0fefe352d64432a8b0015af8ff1eb195cda","tid":1014273,"uid":140523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"舊新聞係超刺激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T05:29:03.000Z","msg":